Bob the Builder for PlayStation Portable.
Just put the folder into the PSP/Game directory and all should be ok. I have tested it on 3.71 33m-3 custom firmware and It should work upto 3.8 33m-5 as well. Not sure on firmware lower or higher than this so you will have to try it for yourself.
